\s Yesu ameingia katika roho yangu
\zon1 1
\zoli1 \bd Yesu\bd*\bd  ameingia katika roho yangu, amenifungulia kamba za dhambi zangu. Tena amenijaza Roho Mtakatifu. Ninamsifu sasa kwa wimbo mpya. \bd*
\pc \bdit Yesu\bdit*\bdit  ni yote kwangu, yote na’pata kwake. Ameondoa dhambi, ametakasa mimi. Shangwe rohoni mwangu ni kama maji mengi, namshukuru sana \bdit*\bdit Mwokozi\bdit*\bdit  wangu. \bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Siku si ndefu tena, kazi si ngumu sasa, njia yanipendeza, ’kiwa nyembamba sana. Katika hali zote ninamwimbia \bd*\bd Yesu\bd*\bd , yeye Mfalme wangu, ninamsifu! \bd*
\pc \bdit Yesu\bdit*\bdit  ni yote kwangu, yote na’pata kwake. Ameondoa dhambi, ametakasa mimi. Shangwe rohoni mwangu ni kama maji mengi, namshukuru sana \bdit*\bdit Mwokozi\bdit*\bdit  wangu. \bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Katika mwendo wangu ninazidishwa shangwe, hata wakinicheka, mwovu akijaribu. Hima \bd*\bd Mwokozi\bd*\bd  wangu atanyakua mimi toka machoni pao. Haleluya! \bd*
